{"word":"G3635 - ὀκνέω - oknéō - ok-neh'-o - Delay","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀκνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">oknéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ok-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Delay</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தாமதமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to feel loath, to be slow; to delay, to hesitate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03BF;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>oknos</b> (<i>hesitation</i>); to <i>be slow</i> (figuratively <i>loath</i>): - delay.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}